{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"provide\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>provide</h1>\n<p>Provides a constant value to the inner route.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">provide</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">](</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The <cite>provide</cite> directive is used as a building block for <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../advanced-topics/custom-directives/#custom-directives\"><em>Custom Directives</em></a> to provide a single value to the\ninner route. To provide several values  use the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../hprovide/#hprovide\"><em>hprovide</em></a> directive.</p>\n<p>See <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../#providedirectives\"><em>Directives to provide values to inner routes</em></a> for an overview of similar directives.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">providePrefixedString</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">provide</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;prefix:&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">providePrefixedString</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;test&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">value</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;prefix:test&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "provide", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/provide", "next": {"link": "../routeRouteResponse/", "title": "routeRouteResponse"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/routeRouteResponse", "routeRouteResponse", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/pass", "pass", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "BasicDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">provide</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../pass/", "title": "pass"}, "metatags": ""}